00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:17,520
 This is the God of the universe who already knows

294
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,320
 what's going to happen in your situation.

295
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:22,040
 This is not a random friend who's observing

296
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:25,320
 what's happening along with you, this is God.

297
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,820
 So that when God tells us not to be afraid,

