00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:32,260
 but also because he gives us reasons

300
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:34,260
 that we shouldn't be afraid.

301
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:36,080
 'Cause fear isn't just something we can just turn off

302
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:39,240
 like a light switch, but fear dies

303
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,920
 when the perception of danger goes away.

304
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:46,920
 Fear can only thrive when the perceived danger seems real,

305
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:48,500
 when the threat seems real.

306
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:50,220
 So God is talking to these people and he's saying,

