00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,520
 But we want to turn from fear

477
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:37,320
 'cause fear is giving our trials

478
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:39,880
 more credit than they deserve.

479
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,360
 Fear is giving our circumstances

