00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,200
 it means more than just he's present.

491
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,040
 'Cause the Bible's clear,

492
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:08,960
 God is present everywhere at the same time.

493
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,880
 He's always present.

494
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:13,240
 So it must mean more than just that.

